<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=no">
		<title>采购信息-<%=baseinfo.matname%></title>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
		<meta name="renderer" content="webkit">
		<meta http-equiv="Cache-Control" content="no-siteapp" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/amazeui.min.css" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/weixin_query.css" />
		<script src="js/jquery.min.js"></script>
		<script src="js/amazeui.min.js"></script>
		<script type="text/javascript" src="js/setting.js"></script>
		<script>
			function setUser(){
				$("#cuser").html(window.localStorage.getItem("user"));
			}
		</script>
	</head>
	<body onload="setUser()">
		<div class="am-panel am-panel-default admin-sidebar-panel">
			<div class="am-panel-bd">
				<p>尊敬的 <span id="cuser"></span> 您好！</p>
				<p>欢迎使用微信版 建定通</p>
				<p>
					<button type="button" class="am-btn am-btn-danger" onclick="window.location='/WXprobase';">工程查询</button>
					<button type="button" class="am-btn am-btn-primary" onclick="window.location='/WXContactBase';">人脉查询</button>
					<button type="button" class="am-btn am-btn-success" onclick="window.location='/WXpromatbase';">采购资讯</button>
				</p>
				<h1>采购详情</h1>
				<table class="am-table am-table-striped am-table-hover jdt-table">
					<tr>
						<td>采购产品名称：</td>
						<td><%=baseinfo.matname%></td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>信息发布日期：</td>
						<td><%=baseinfo.ptime%></td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>当前状态：</td>
						<td>采购进行中</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>所属工程项目名称：</td>
						<td><a href="/WXProDetail?id=<%=baseinfo.proid%>"><%=baseinfo.proname%></a></td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>计量单位：</td>
						<td><%=baseinfo.matunit%></td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>要求品牌：</td>
						<td>不限</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>产品型号：</td>
						<td>未透露</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>产品规格：</td>
						<td>未透露</td>
					</tr>
					
					<tr>
						<td>备注：</td>
						<td>无</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>采购总量：</td>
						<td>未透露</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>采购方采购单价：</td>
						<td>未透露</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>采购起始日期：</td>
						<td><%=baseinfo.stime%></td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>采购截止日期：</td>
						<td><%=baseinfo.ftime%></td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>成交供应商：</td>
						<td><%=baseinfo.gycompany%></td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>已成交总量：</td>
						<td>未透露</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>成交单价：</td>
						<td>未透露</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>成交日期：</td>
						<td>未透露</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>采购负责人：</td>
						<td><a href="/WXContactinfo?id=<%=baseinfo.pepid%>"><%=baseinfo.linkname%></a></td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>采购负责人所属公司</td>
						<td><a href="/WXcompany?id=<%=baseinfo.pcid%>"><%=baseinfo.company%></a></td>
					</tr>
				</table>
			</div>
		</div>
		
	</body>
</html>